name: If Zine+1 print
description:
IF zine and 1 8" x 10" print of your choice.
1 in 4

Legendary Graffiti writer Trap IF announces the release of his first zine entitled, Ikonik Figure Volume Zero, 
The first to be released in a set of four, this zine is full color, offset print, and contains over 40 pages of non-stop realness. Included are over 150 original images of the IF crew from the 1970’s to the present day. Featuring paint from writers Jick, Enuf, Shone, Trap, and more. In collaboration with Queens based graphic designer Patrick Sullivan, this production includes photos from the libraries of some of New York’s best writers. A brief narrative has been provided by Trap detailing stories behind select photography and the New York graffiti scene.
